quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  28,60,"Uye chero chii chamakapuhwa rufaro rwehupenyu hwepano pasi uye chishongedzo chawo, uye izvo zvina Allah (hupenyu hwemangwana) zviri nani uye hazviperi. Asi hamufungewo here"
  28,61,"Asi uyu watakavimbisa vimbiso tsvene (Paradhiso), iyo yaachawana iri yechokwadi, akafanana here neuyo watakaita kuti ave anofarira hupenyu hwepano pasi, uye nemusi wekumutswa achava pakati peavo vanounzwa (kunorangwa muGehena)"
  28,62,"Uye (rangarirai) zuva apo vachave (Allah) vanovadaidza vachiti: “Varipi avo (vamaiti) vabetseri vangu vamaitungamidza?”"
  28,63,"Kune avo shoko richaita chokwadi kwavari (kuti varangwe) vachati: “Tenzi vedu! Ava ndivo vatakarasisa. Takavarasisa, semarasikiro ataivewo takaita. Tinoramba mhosva (kubva kwavari) pamberi penyu. Handisu vavainamata.”"
  28,64,"Uye zvichanzi (kwavari): “Daidzai avo vabatsiri venyu”, uye vachavadaidza, asi havavape mhinduro, uye vachaona marwadzo. (Vachave vanoshuvira kuti) dai vaive vakatungamirwa"
  28,65,"Uye (rangarirai) zuva iro (Allah) ravachadaidza vachiti: “Ndeipi mhinduro yamakapa vatumwa?”"
  28,66,"Saka nhau (dzemhinduro yakanaka) dzichavanzika kwavari pazuva iroro, uye havazokwanisa kubvunzana"
  28,67,"Asi kune uyo akareurura, akatenda (muIslaam), uye akaita mabasa akanaka, achave pakati pevanhu vakabudirira"
  28,68,"Uye Tenzi vako vanosika icho chinhu chavanoda nekusarudza, uye (vanhu) havana sarudzo yavanayo (pachinhu chipi zvacho). Allah ndivo muyemurwi, uye ndivo vari pamusoro pane izvo zvavanosanganisa (sevabatsiri vavo)"
  28,69,"Uye Allah vanoziva izvo zvavanoviga mumoyo yavo, uye zvavanoburitsa"
  28,70,"Uye ndiAllah: Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna chimwe chinhu chine kodzero yekunamatwa kunze kwavo). Kwavari ndiko kune rumbidzo dzese nekutendwa kwose mukutanga (pasi pano) uye mukupedzisira (muhupenyu hwemangwana). Uye ndivo vanotonga, uye kwavari ndiko kwamuchadzorerwa"